0.0105 Saturn mass (Saturn has 95.16 Earth masses)[3]
0.0583 Neptune mass (Neptune has 17.147 Earth masses)[4]
0.000 003 003 Solar mass (\\(M_{\\odot}\\)) (The Sun has 332946 Earth masses)"""^^ns1:LatexString .

